<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ein
                            <expan>frewntlich<ex>er</ex></expan> tag gemachet was
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hilpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Prunne und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gen <expan>Perching<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        auf den <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> montag cze nacht do cze sein, und
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, dar czü <expan>cze kume<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        wan wir ew gar <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> dabey
                            <expan>seh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch in den
                            <expan>teydinge<ex>n</ex></expan> czü
                            <expan>Rege<ex>n</ex>sp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> geredt
                            <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, daz ir auf des
                                <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teil dabey sein süllet,
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag hat uns
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Hilpolt <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>widerbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> briefe;
                        und darauf <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und einen <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        bescheiden acht tag darnach, als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czü
                                <expan>Rege<ex>n</ex>sp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> geteydingt ist, also
                        <add>daz</add> der tag nu sein sol, <app><note><q type="date">auf den
                            <expan>nehst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> montag cze nacht vor sant
                            <expan>Mert<ex>ein</ex></expan> tag</q>09.11.1411</note></app> czü
                            <expan>Perching<ex>en</ex></expan> cze sein und des morgens auf den
                        eritag die sache cze handeln. Nu <expan>bit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr edel
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleizz, daz ir also czü <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet. Das
                            <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat</expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
